title: "Google Agrees to $700 Million Settlement in Play Store Case"
text: "Google will pay $700 million to settle an antitrust suit involving its Play store. The tech giant announced the settlement Monday (Dec. 18)
source_name: revealing the details of a September agreement in a 2020 suit by the U.S. government and several states."

title: "Apple plans rescue for $17 billion watch business in face of ban"
